So, who are you going to main this season? Also I just wanted to say I am humbled by the love and support in the community since the launch of this game. Whether you’re a streamer, casual player, pro.. or just stopping by from the explore page. No matter who you are I’m grateful for your presence and the amount of time you spend visiting my page. Watching people’s hard work be presented to the community is what I like to show, being a platform is a great humble incentive for myself, being able to see so many people grow since the launch of this game has been amazing! I hope to continue this and create more opportunities for smaller people to grow within the community! ❤️
